&lt;li&gt;Cover institutional clients in a sales trading capacity, acting as a trusted point of contact for order flow, market color, and trading ideas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage Galaxy Securities’ unique position as a broker-dealer within a crypto-native firm to develop innovative cross-asset products and solutions for institutional clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

