&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Galaxy is a global leader in digital assets and data center infrastructure, delivering solutions that accelerate progress in finance and artificial intelligence. We believe that blockchain and digital asset innovation will transform how value moves through the world – and we’re building the products and services to make that future a reality.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Our institutional digital assets platform spans trading, investment banking, asset management, staking, self-custody, and tokenization technology. We also invest in and operate cutting-edge data center infrastructure to power AI and high-performance computing, addressing the growing demand for scalable energy and compute in the U.S.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;We work at the intersection of finance and technology, helping institutions, startups, and developers navigate a digitally native economy. Led by CEO and Founder Michael Novogratz, our team blends deep crypto expertise with institutional experience and a shared commitment to shaping the future of Web3 and AI.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Galaxy is headquartered in New York City, with offices across North America, Europe, the Middle East, and Asia.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;To learn more about our businesses and products, visit www.galaxy.com.&lt;/p&gt;
